WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:04.260
What if this life is the one that we begged for?

00:00:06.080 --> 00:00:08.980
What if my higher power let me come back

00:00:10.120 --> 00:00:12.700
so that I could see the mountains again?

00:00:14.680 --> 00:00:17.220
Be on the lake while the sun kissed me?

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:23.180
Laugh with my friends until my stomach hurts.

00:00:25.800 --> 00:00:29.180
Get my heart broken over and over.

00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:34.580
Cry uncontrollably in the shower

00:00:36.920 --> 00:00:39.700
by myself. Flowers a thousand more times.

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:44.540
Your beautiful song for the first time.
